title: Congress reportedly investigating possible intel lapses over Russian presence in Syria
text: U.S. lawmakers have begun investigating possible intelligence lapses related to Russia's ongoing military action in Syria, it was reported early Thursday, as NATO defense ministers held a crisis meeting in Brussels. ...
